Mount Ulap.Name: Mount Ulap
Mount Ulap.Description: Mount Ulap is a 7.7 kilometer moderately trafficked point-to-point trail located near Tuba, Benguet, Philippines that offers the chance to see wildlife and is rated as moderate. The trail is primarily used for hiking.

Comments.Author: Adam Jones
Comments.Comment: Honestly one of the beset experiences ever, took us a while to figure out how to get there but it was amazing.

Comments.Author: Isaac Dylan
Comments.Comment: Traveling changes you as a person, you gain more perspective, this is the perfect spot to do that.

Comments.Author: Hudson Luca
Comments.Comment: Definitely recommend going there, not too far and not a lot of people toi ruin the experience.
